%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (JDBC/Python)
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider
    participant Polaris as Polaris Catalog
    participant S3 as S3 Storage

    Client->>Coord: Flight SQL Handshake (user/pass)
    Coord->>OIDC: Password Grant (user/pass)
    OIDC-->>Coord: JWT Bearer Token
    Coord-->>Client: Session Token (JWT)

    Client->>Coord: SQL Query
    Coord->>Polaris: LoadTable (JWT in Authorization header)
    Polaris-->>Coord: Table metadata + S3 credentials (scoped to user)
    Coord->>S3: Read Parquet files (user-scoped credentials)
    S3-->>Coord: Data
    Coord-->>Client: Arrow RecordBatches
